title: Timecry (2008)
description:
Timecry EP with cover.


Timecry is a swedish cosmic death-metal band from Gothenburg.
There line up is: 

The Roy - vocals
Ludvig - Guitars
Magnus - Guitars
Chris - Bass
Johan - Drums

Songs:

"Better Die Standing"
Music by: Timecry

Music by: Timecry 
Lyrics: The Roy

Music by: Timecry 
Lyrics: The Roy

"Never More"
Music by: Timecry 
Lyrics: The Roy
